r <token> header\n- Unauthenticated requests to protected routes must get 401\n- All tenant data routes require auth\n- The schema.sql file has the CREATE TABLE statements - read it and use those exact table/column names\n- tsconfig uses strict mode, ES2022, Node16 modules - use proper imports with .js extensions for local modules\n- ESLint rule: no unused vars (except those prefixed with _)\n\nSTRUCTURE SUGGESTION:\n- src/app.ts - createApp function, Express app setup\n- src/db.ts - database initialization, run schema.sql\n- src/middleware/auth.ts - JWT auth middleware  \n- src/routes/auth.ts - register, login, profile, role change\n- src/routes/events.ts - event ingestion\n- src/routes/query.ts - count, timeseries, breakdown\n- src/routes/dashboards.ts - CRUD\n- src/routes/export.ts - CSV and JSON export\n\nIMPORTANT TYPESCRIPT NOTES:\n- Use import/export with .js extensions for local modules (Node16 module resolution)\n- Use express.json() middleware\n- Type the Request objects properly\n- Make sure no unused variables (prefix unused with _)\n\nAfter implementing, run: npm run build && npm run lint\nFix any errors. Don't stop until both pass.\" -y 2>&1","description":"Dispatch full implementation to Gemini","timeout":600000},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":266,"cache_read_input_tokens":21608,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":266},"output_tokens":24,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d95683e4-30eb-48fb-943e-47ac735c729e","uuid":"1ecf6f02-1351-44d4-ac06-5b4742c8264d"}
